description: [``botocore``] This release for Amazon ECR Public makes several change to bring the SDK into sync with the API.

[``botocore``] Introducing Amazon Kendra Intelligent Ranking, a new set of Kendra APIs that leverages Kendra semantic ranking capabilities to improve the quality of search results from other search services (i.e. OpenSearch, ElasticSearch, Solr).
[``botocore``] Network Firewall now supports the Suricata rule action reject, in addition to the actions pass, drop, and alert.
[``botocore``] Enabled FIPS aws-us-gov endpoints in SDK.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for a new portal authentication type: AWS IAM Identity Center (successor to AWS Single Sign-On).
